			Company Description 


			IBC Advanced Alloys Corp. is a manufacturer and distributor of rare metals (beryllium) based alloys and related products. It operates its business through the following segments: copper alloys, engineered materials, and corporate. The company was founded on December 11, 2002 and is headquartered in ...
		


                IBC Advanced Alloys Corp. is a manufacturer and distributor of rare metals (beryllium) based alloys and related products. It operates its business through the following segments: copper alloys, engineered materials, and corporate. The company was founded on December 11, 2002 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
            




